sentences.english: Pseudopodia are characteristic of many dipterous larvae.
sentences.chinese: 伪足为多数双翅目幼虫所特有。

sentences.english: We describe the influence of heavy metal pollution on the morphological and internal structural changes of aquatic Dipteral insects.
sentences.chinese: 水生双翅目昆虫是监测水体重金属污染的理想对象。

sentences.english: Because of their importance in these systems, aquatic dipterans are ideal candidates to monitor water heavy metal pollution.

sentences.english: The mode of action of precocene on ovarian development of dipteran insect is discussed.
sentences.chinese: 本文还对早熟素作用于双翅目昆虫的方式作了讨论。

definition: Lepidoptera (insect order including butterflies 蝶類|蝶类 and moths 蛾類|蛾类)
Hymenoptera (insect order including ants and bees)
Hemiptera (suborder of order Homoptera, insects including cicadas and aphids)
Homoptera (insect suborder including cicadas, aphids, plant-hoppers, shield bugs etc)
Orthoptera (insect order including grasshoppers, crickets and locusts)
Odonata, order consisting of about 6,000 species of dragonflies and damselflies
